\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ezw1665703530124.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ezw1665703530124.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ezw1665703530124.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ezw1665703530124\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Displays the contents of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerrorcontext</span> whenever a ProcScript error occurs (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span>&lt; 0).\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__p_d175682e1_d175683e1_d175684e1\">The <span class=\"keyword wintitle\">Error Context</span> window shows\n         the context of only the latest ProcScript error.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__section_cxv_ks3_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d236820e66\">Topic items</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Displays the topic items of the latest ProcScript error, that is, the constant parts of\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerrorcontext</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__p_d175694e1_d175695e1_d175696e1\">These items are:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__ul_hbh_ns3_1xb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__li_d53543e1_d53544e1_d53545e1\">ERROR </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__li_d53546e1_d53547e1_d53548e1\">MNEM </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__li_d53549e1_d53550e1_d53551e1\">Description </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__li_d53552e1_d53553e1_d53554e1\">Component </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__li_d53555e1_d53556e1_d53557e1\">Procname </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__li_d53558e1_d53559e1_d53560e1\">Trigger </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__li_d53561e1_d53562e1_d53563e1\">Line </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__li_d53564e1_d53565e1_d53566e1\">ADDITIONAL </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ezw1665703530124__section_dr5_ns3_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d236820e109\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Displays a short description of each topic item of the ProcScript error. This\n            description is the variable part of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerrorcontext</span> associative\n            list.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/opq1665702649630.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$procerrorcontext</a><p>Return the location of the error specified by $procerror.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ypd1665702576258.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$procerror</a><p>Return the reason for an error in ProcScript execution.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527412\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527412\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Error Context Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Displays the contents of $procerrorcontext whenever a ProcScript error occurs ( $procerror < 0). The Error Context window shows the context of only the latest ProcScript error. Topic items Displays the topic items of the latest ProcScript error, that is, the constant parts of $procerrorcontext . These items are: ERROR MNEM Description Component Procname Trigger Line ADDITIONAL Description Displays a short description of each topic item of the ProcScript error. This description is the variable part of the $procerrorcontext associative list. Related Links $procerrorcontext Return the location of the error specified by $procerror. $procerror Return the reason for an error in ProcScript execution. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}